[
    {
        "text": "Yay! I’ve won again, Tia!",
        "start": 23.44,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "Wow, Tofu!",
        "start": 27.64,
        "duration": 1.32
    },
    {
        "text": "You’ve really become good at this game",
        "start": 29.4,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you want to play one more round with me?",
        "start": 32.72,
        "duration": 2.52
    },
    {
        "text": "The winner gets the loser’s share of mom’s special pie.",
        "start": 36.6,
        "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
        "text": "MOM! ",
        "start": 42.64,
        "duration": 0.64
    },
    {
        "text": "Tofu! Look at the time! ",
        "start": 46.84,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "We’ve not completed any of our chores",
        "start": 49.04,
        "duration": 2.84
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, don’t worry about it Tia. ",
        "start": 53.04,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "It’s a Sunday.",
        "start": 55.72,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "We’ll just tell mom that we forgot",
        "start": 57.4,
        "duration": 2.32
    },
    {
        "text": "But we remember now. ",
        "start": 60.88,
        "duration": 1.48
    },
    {
        "text": "We should do it now. ",
        "start": 62.6,
        "duration": 1.48
    },
    {
        "text": "Umm…",
        "start": 65.12,
        "duration": 1.04
    },
    {
        "text": "do we have to?",
        "start": 66.68,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "Mom won’t know.",
        "start": 68.68,
        "duration": 1.32
    },
    {
        "text": "Tofu! ",
        "start": 71.32,
        "duration": 0.76
    },
    {
        "text": "Are you suggesting that we should lie to mom? ",
        "start": 72.52,
        "duration": 3.56
    },
    {
        "text": "And who will lie to her?",
        "start": 79.04,
        "duration": 1.92
    },
    {
        "text": "Ummmm…",
        "start": 82.12,
        "duration": 1.44
    },
    {
        "text": "That’s the worst idea you’ve ever had Tofu",
        "start": 85.96,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "And you’re talking like the little mouse",
        "start": 89.64,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "The little who?",
        "start": 94.6,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": "Belling The Cat",
        "start": 97.16,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "Thats a story that i want to tell you in this context",
        "start": 99.32,
        "duration": 4.04
    },
    {
        "text": "Once upon a time ",
        "start": 122.36,
        "duration": 1.4
    },
    {
        "text": "the many mice that lived in his store troubled a grocer",
        "start": 124.88,
        "duration": 4.4
    },
    {
        "text": "These mice are spoiling every thing.",
        "start": 131.6,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "Today they pierced holes in the grain bags",
        "start": 134.48,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh, dear! ",
        "start": 138.88,
        "duration": 0.8
    },
    {
        "text": "What should we do?",
        "start": 140.76,
        "duration": 1.2
    },
    {
        "text": "I don’t know. ",
        "start": 143.0,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "if the villagers find out ",
        "start": 144.12,
        "duration": 1.96
    },
    {
        "text": "they will stop coming to the store and buying things from me",
        "start": 146.28,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh no! What will we do then? ",
        "start": 150.68,
        "duration": 2.88
    },
    {
        "text": "Our business will be disrupted entirely ",
        "start": 154.04,
        "duration": 3.36
    },
    {
        "text": "I agree",
        "start": 157.96,
        "duration": 0.96
    },
    {
        "text": "Oh! I have an idea!",
        "start": 160.28,
        "duration": 2.48
    },
    {
        "text": "Why don’t you get a cat for the store?",
        "start": 163.68,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "A good, strong cat will eat the mice away quickly",
        "start": 166.88,
        "duration": 4.88
    },
    {
        "text": "And new mice will be afraid to enter the store",
        "start": 172.28,
        "duration": 3.76
    },
    {
        "text": "out of her fear. ",
        "start": 176.04,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Hmmm",
        "start": 177.96,
        "duration": 1.16
    },
    {
        "text": "That’s a brilliant idea!",
        "start": 179.12,
        "duration": 1.88
    },
    {
        "text": " I will get one",
        "start": 181.6,
        "duration": 1.48
    },
    {
        "text": "first thing tomorrow. ",
        "start": 183.32,
        "duration": 1.32
    },
    {
        "text": "The next morning",
        "start": 193.56,
        "duration": 1.12
    },
    {
        "text": "the grocer went and got a big strong cat for his store\n ",
        "start": 194.68,
        "duration": 5.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Just as his wife had said",
        "start": 211.52,
        "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
        "text": "she pounced at the first sight of mice.",
        "start": 213.92,
        "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
        "text": "The mice were taken by surprise.",
        "start": 219.32,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "Our brothers have been attacked and eaten up by this cat",
        "start": 224.08,
        "duration": 3.44
    },
    {
        "text": " that the grocer has brought",
        "start": 227.52,
        "duration": 1.76
    },
    {
        "text": "We all should be careful from now on",
        "start": 229.64,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "As the days passed",
        "start": 235.96,
        "duration": 1.72
    },
    {
        "text": "the movement of the mice became restricted",
        "start": 240.92,
        "duration": 3.12
    },
    {
        "text": "They always lived in fear of the cat ",
        "start": 245.0,
        "duration": 3.08
    },
    {
        "text": "and were unable to get food ",
        "start": 248.24,
        "duration": 2.16
    },
    {
        "text": "and supplies for their families from the store.",
        "start": 250.6,
        "duration": 2.96
    },
    {
        "text": "If any of them ventured out",
        "start": 254.96,
        "duration": 2.12
    },
    {
        "text": " the cat ",
        "start": 257.8,
        "duration": 0.64
    },
    {
        "text": "ate them",
        "start": 259.12,
        "duration": 1.08
    },
    {
        "text": "This distressed the mice very much. ",
        "start": 262.88,
        "duration": 2.8
    },
    {
        "text": "They made many plans to avoid and escape the cat but failed miserably.",
        "start": 266.28,
        "duration": 6.64
    },
    {
        "text": "We are losing our brothers and sisters to this cat",
        "start": 275.16,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
    {
        "text": "Something must be done. ",
        "start": 279.28,
        "duration": 2.04
    },
    {
        "text": "I have a simple plan ",
        "start": 282.72,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "but I am sure it will be successful. ",
        "start": 284.8,
        "duration": 2.76
    },
    {
        "text": "We just have to put a bell around the cat’s neck",
        "start": 290.32,
        "duration": 3.32
    },
    {
        "text": "Every time the cat will move",
        "start": 297.88,
        "duration": 2.2
    },
    {
        "text": "we will hear the bell ring first. ",
        "start": 300.52,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "This will give us enough time to escape her.",
        "start": 303.84,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "That’s a very good idea. ",
        "start": 308.4,
        "duration": 1.64
    },
    {
        "text": "Good thinking, brother",
        "start": 311.36,
        "duration": 1.68
    },
    {
        "text": "we should arrange a bell immediately",
        "start": 313.04,
        "duration": 3.16
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes, I agree",
        "start": 317.6,
        "duration": 1.84
    },
    {
        "text": "This is a very good plan. ",
        "start": 320.04,
        "duration": 2.6
    },
    {
        "text": "But I have just one question ",
        "start": 323.28,
        "duration": 2.24
    },
    {
        "text": "who will bell the cat",
        "start": 326.12,
        "duration": 2.0
    },
    {
        "text": "Suddenly there fell a hush over the excited mice ",
        "start": 329.52,
        "duration": 4.64
    },
    {
        "text": "because none of them had the answer to the question",
        "start": 334.36,
        "duration": 3.52
    },
    {
        "text": "None had the courage to risk his own life to bell the cat. ",
        "start": 338.84,
        "duration": 4.88
    },
    {
        "text": "And so it remained that the cat was never belled",
        "start": 344.68,
        "duration": 4.32
    },
    {
        "text": "So you see Tofu",
        "start": 351.4,
        "duration": 1.8
    },
    {
        "text": "it is one thing to just give out ideas ",
        "start": 353.96,
        "duration": 3.24
    },
    {
        "text": "and another to actually go ahead and do as you’ve said",
        "start": 357.32,
        "duration": 4.72
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes, Tia",
        "start": 363.4,
        "duration": 1.28
    },
    {
        "text": " I am ashamed of what I suggested",
        "start": 365.04,
        "duration": 2.92
    },
    {
        "text": "I said it without considering whether it was right or wrong ",
        "start": 370.52,
        "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
        "text": "and possible or impossible",
        "start": 375.2,
        "duration": 2.56
    },
    {
        "text": "Come, let’s go and finish off the chores. ",
        "start": 380.16,
        "duration": 3.8
    },
    {
        "text": "I am glad you understood that Tofu.",
        "start": 385.12,
        "duration": 2.4
    },
    {
        "text": "Now, let’s start with putting away these games. ",
        "start": 388.28,
        "duration": 3.36
    }
]